msgid "KDE Linux"
msgstr "KDE Linux"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.linux.metainfo.xml:9
msgid ""
"A modern Linux distribution focused on the KDE Plasma desktop environment"
msgstr ""
"Šiuolaikinis Linux platinamasis paketas, kurio dėmesys sutelktas į KDE "
"Plasma darbalaukio aplinką"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.linux.metainfo.xml:14
msgid ""
"KDE Linux is a user-friendly operating system built around the KDE Plasma "
"desktop environment. It provides a complete computing experience with a "
"focus on productivity, customization, and ease of use."
msgstr ""
"KDE Linux yra patogi operacinė sistema, sukurta remiantis KDE Plasma "
"darbalaukio aplinka. Ji pateikia pilnavertį naudojimosi kompiuteriu "
"patyrimą, skirdama daug dėmesio produktyvumui, tinkinimui ir lengvam "
"naudojimui."

